name: Misaka Mikoto (Toaru series)「とあるシリーズ・御坂美琴」
description:
Please use the final version for the best experience

If you have any suggestions or want to report some bugs, please leave a message here or send me an email（shakan0415@gmail.com）. In order to avoid ambiguity in understanding, the email should be written in English, Japanese, Chinese, or Korean.

This maybe the final version of this Lora. I fixed the swimsuit bug, and now you can make the image of Misaka Mikoto wearing her winter school uniform.

In order to make the generated character closer to the real Misaka Mikoto, I added a lot of animation screenshots in this version of the material, which may cause the expression to not be obvious when the expression is not selected.

Do not forget the trigger word "misaka mikoto"

And the following are the keywords of various clothing

uniform(summer)

school uniform, tokiwadai school uniform, shirt, white shirt, sweater vest, skirt, v-neck, pleated skirt, short sleeves, brown sweater vest, dress shirt, shorts, grey skirt, socks, collared shirt, shoes, loose socks, shorts under skirt, loafers, brown footwear, black skirt, short shorts

swimsuit

multicolored swimsuit, swimsuit, competition swimsuit,  barefoot, bare shoulders, black one-piece swimsuit, collarbone, one-piece swimsuit, sleeveless,

gym uniform

bare shoulders, collarbone, gym uniform, sleeveless, sleeveless shirt, white shorts, white socks, sneakers,short shorts,

uniform(winter)

bowtie, brown jacket, red bow, red bowtie,blazer, bow, school uniform， skirt, pleated skirt, shorts, grey skirt, socks,shoes, loose socks, shorts under skirt, loafers, brown footwear, black skirt, short shorts

Of course, you can also customize unique clothing according to your preferences.

About EASY VERSION:

You can enter only one keyword misaka mikoto to get a result of misaka mikoto in summer school uniform byEASY VERSION. Although this saves trouble, it also means that it is difficult for you to design unique clothing that you like for misaka mikoto

About OLD VERSION:

You can adjust this lora arbitrarily, but if you want to get an authentic misaka mikoto, I recommend you use the following prompt

common (head)

  new_misaka_mikoto,1girl,solo,misaka mikoto,brown hair,brown eyes,white flower hair ornament,short hair, small breasts, bangs,hair between eyes,collarbone,

summer uniform

tokiwadai school uniform,pleated skirt,white v-neck collared dress shirt,short sleeves,grey miniskirt,brown sweater vest,white short shorts under skirt,brown loafers,white loose socks,

About OLD VERSION V2:

Compared with the OLD VERSION, V2 has added keywords for gym suits and swimwear, but the effect of swimwear is not stable. It is recommended to use the final version to get the best experience.

I would greatly appreciate it if you could provide me with a cup of coffee as a gesture of encouragement to motivate me to further improve this Lora:https://www.buymeacoffee.com/ShakanOji
